Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.84,0:50:52.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,现在我们谈论一些古老的历史，我会暂时更新它
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.74,0:50:57.86,English,,0,0,0,,But classically you either use static content meaning a fixed web page
